'''愛丁堡電車'''（{{lang-en|Edinburgh Trams}}）是[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]城市[[愛丁堡|愛丁堡]]的有軌電車系統<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.heraldscotland.com/news/transport/after-eight-years-of-chaos-citys-pound700m-trams-project-is-stopped-in-its-tracks.14848264 |title=After eight years of chaos, city's £700m trams project is stopped in its tracks |work=The Herald |accessdate=15 September 2013 |first=Damien |last=Henderson |archive-date=2013-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131228002800/http://www.heraldscotland.com/news/transport/after-eight-years-of-chaos-citys-pound700m-trams-project-is-stopped-in-its-tracks.14848264 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，由{{link-en|愛丁堡交通局|Transport for Edinburgh}}營運。愛丁堡電車現在有一條路線，全長{{convert|14|km|mi}}，往返於[[愛丁堡新城|愛丁堡新城]]的約克宮和[[愛丁堡機場|愛丁堡機場]]，共16站。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-edinburgh-east-fife-38265174 |title=New Edinburgh Gateway interchange opens in capital |work=BBC |date=11 December 2016 |accessdate=22 December 2016 |archive-date=2017-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510152429/http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-edinburgh-east-fife-38265174 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 愛丁堡電車開工於2008年6月，工程一度延宕，最終於2014年5月31日通車。

